<ul>

<li>Drivers may cancel routes if necessary.</li>

<li>Passengers should contact the driver if travel plans change.</li>

</ul>

<h3>5. Privacy</h3>

<p>
User information is kept secure and is used only for providing transport services.
</p>

<h3>6. Data Retention Policy</h3>

<ul>

<li>Booking records are automatically deleted after <strong>48 hours (2 days)</strong>.</li>

